{"tid":759724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隱形股神愛儲「紙股票」1.08萬炒到億億聲","createTime":"2018-07-29T01:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T05:25:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0611460c42cc3358702a12a6b1a2a9bc07d77157","tid":759724,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:42:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180729/20463078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F20463078&d=EiDfJdQdG%2FZi7HAVwIfDtJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=47899b4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F20463078&h=721d99ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180729/20463078</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月29日 <br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\n隱形股神愛儲「紙股票」1.08萬炒到億億聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【財經人物】寫投資的書坊間有很多，自稱股神的人也不少，但能夠將辦公室改裝成股票收藏室，將數千張股票封箱，再以字母分門別類，方便翻查，相信只此一人。<br />\n<br />\n投資股票三十年的Henry Chan白手興家，小時候一家八口住板間房，典型的獅子山下故事，由買第一隻股票置地開始，他從較冷門的供股中參透搵錢秘訣，進而在股票市場以各種投資工具賺錢，藍籌、細價股、莊家股、供股及近年賺得最多的新股，每一類，他都有自己的獨門理解。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【一周必看】行車記錄儀有Display分分鐘犯法？<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【一周必看】奧斯爾難忍歧視退出國家隊「贏波就係德國人輸波就係移民」"},{"pid":"4ebff9dc4e3a3c43f334b0d0cada1813fd13fb65","tid":759724,"uid":29930,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1萬變1億"},{"pid":"af053b6e47ae6362154b318b0440d7a6240efd02","tid":759724,"uid":20241,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17